</span></li></ul><p class="sc-FNXRL jGHEAN pf-2646_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-gyElHZ fxaypC pf-2648_">It is vital to prioritise training to reap advantages while mitigating the disadvantages associated with inadequate or incomplete refresher statutory and mandatory health and social care training.<br><br><a href="https://www.mandatorytraining.co.uk/blogs/dr-richard-dune/what-is-the-guidance-on-statutory-and-mandatory-training" target="_blank"><i><span style="color: rgb(0, 71, 178);">Find out more about health and social care compliance requirements</span></i></a>.<br>

